<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="nl">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Bedankt</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background: #f4f4f4; margin: 0; padding: 40px 20px; }
    .wrap { max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto; background: #fff; padding: 32px; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.08); text-align: center; }
    a { color: #111; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrap">
    <h1>Bedankt</h1>
    <p>Je CV is succesvol verstuurd.</p>
    <p><a href="/">Terug naar het formulier</a></p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
